âœ… **Automated Image Generation** â†’ Converts a script into a sequence of images  
âœ… **Optimized for Shorts (9:16 format)** â†’ Can be changed for different video formats  
âœ… **Supports Large Scripts** â†’ Can generate **up to 1,000 images**  
âœ… **Customizable AI Models** â†’ Uses `gpt-4o-mini` but can be replaced  
âœ… **Flexible Image Quality** â†’ Depends on **prompt quality** & AI model  
âœ… **Fast & Efficient** â†’ Uses **Replicateâ€™s Flux-Schnell** model  

![AI Generated Example](images/ai_generated_example.jpg)

