## **ðŸ›  How It Works**
1. **Enter Your Story/Script** â†’ The script analyzes the story and extracts key scenes.  
2. **Generate Image Prompts** â†’ OpenAI creates **realistic, cinematic** image prompts.  
3. **Create Images with Replicate** â†’ The script sends prompts to the **Flux-Schnell model** on Replicate.  
4. **Download & Save Images** â†’ The images are resized and saved as high-quality JPG files.  

ðŸ”¹ **By default, the aspect ratio is set to 9:16 for YouTube Shorts, but it can be changed.**  
ðŸ”¹ **The AI model (`gpt-4o-mini`) can be replaced with other OpenAI models.**  

